{{zh-forms|[[食之无味，弃之可惜]]|[[食]][[之]][[無]][[味]]，[[棄]][[之]][[可惜]]}}
==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: shí zhī wú wèi, qì zhī kĕxí
===Etymology===
Literally: some food may lack flavor, but it would still be a pity to throw it away
===Idiom===
# some things have no apparent value, but one still can't bear to throw them away
#: ''[[李]][[嘉]][[誠心]][[有]][[不]][[甘]][[棄]]20[[年]][[夢想]] '''食之無味棄之可惜'''''[http://72.14.235.104/search?q=cache:lNtYT6ctagsJ:www.tynews.com.cn/dibu_content/2005-03/10/content_784552.htm+%22%E9%A3%9F%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%A0%E5%91%B3%EF%BC%8C%E5%BC%83%E4%B9%8B%E5%8F%AF%E6%83%9C%22+site:.cn&hl=zh-CN&gl=cn&ct=clnk&cd=5]
#: ''Li Jia sincerely did not wish to let go of a twenty year dream of his, '''he just could not bear to part with it'''.''
